    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>chestnut</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong> into quarters</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1676388199342-x200.jpg",
