            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>carrot</strong>,<strong> diced potatoes</strong>,<strong> chopped mushrooms </strong>and <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and 350ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [455ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[650ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1676388203779-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1676388203779-x400.jpg",
