          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1676388203779-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, cover the dish with a lid and put it in the oven for an initial 25 min or until the vegetables are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Use the rest of the cooking time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1676388208428-x200.jpg",
