            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1676388208428-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 25 min, add your <strong>blanched peas</strong>,<strong> soft cheese </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven, covered, for a final 5 min or until the peas are warmed through – this is your <strong>one-pot creamy chicken & vegetable fricassée</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
