      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, taste the <strong>one-pot creamy chicken & vegetable fricassée </strong>for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> as needed</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>all over</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
